Julian Morris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julian_Morris 0 Julian David Morris (born 13 January 1983) is an English-American actor. After appearing in the British television series The Knock (1996) and Fish (2000) during his teenage years, he had his first starring role in the American horror film Cry Wolf (2005). He subsequently had supporting roles in the thriller Donkey Punch (2008), the historical drama Valkyrie (2008), and the slasher film Sorority Row (2009). Morris has also appeared in American television as a series regular on Pretty Little Liars and Hand of God. He also had recurring roles on Once Upon a Time and New Girl.
